	<div id="container-how-to-apply">
		<h1>How do I apply?</h1>
		<p><b>Step 1.. Drive by:</b> Please drive by the property to be sure that the neighborhood and building and its yard and parking suit the needs of your family. There is a map showing the location of the property on the property page. If you like the location please move on to step two.</p>
		<p><b>Step 2.. Showing:</b> We do not set appointments for showing a property because we work on a first come first served basis. If you are interested in seeing the interior of the property, call me at 605-341-3404. You may call at anytime. We will normally meet you at the property with-in 30 minutes. ALL persons (age 18 or older) should be at the showing.&nbsp;You need to be in a position to&nbsp;complete the&nbsp;application and pay the deposit at the time of showing. So do not forget to bring your check book and photo ID to the showing.</p>
		<p><b>Step 3.. Complete our application:</b> At the end of the showing, you will complete the rental application while at the property. <b>WE CAN NOT HOLD A PROPERTY FOR YOU WITHOUT THE COMPLETED APPLICATION AND DEPOSITS AMOUNTS PAID.</b></p>
